  Description: As the only team still using their original outdoor practice field, 
    the Oklahoma Stoppers prepare ruthlessly in the wind, rain, and snow.  Anything
    can happen in a Zone Shot match,  so this coaching staff keeps their eyes on
    making sure their players  stay sharp and ready for whatever is thrown their
    way.  This squad places their focus on starting strong and never looking back. 
    Their mindset is to work their way inside for a big score  and trust their defense
    to finish the job.
  CoachName: Nicko Demus
